UK money market forecasts 1 . 2 bln stg shortage . The average of forecasts by UK money market brokers of today ' s market shortage is 1 . 2 billion stg , according to a Reuter market survey . The official forecast for the shortage will be released by the Bank of England at between 0845 GMT and 0900 GMT . Yesterday ' s final shortage was 1 . 5 bln stg . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7715 
